{"word":"G4400 - προχειρίζομαι - procheirízomai - prokh-i-rid'-zom-ahee - Choose","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προχειρίζομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">procheirízomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">prokh-i-rid'-zom-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Choose</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தெரிந்துகொள், ஏற்படுத்து"},{"paragraph":"to put into the hand, to deliver into the hands"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G4253 - πρό - pró - pro/4253\">G4253</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G5495 - χείρ - cheír - khire/5495\">G5495</a>; to <i>handle</i> for oneself <i>in advance</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>purpose:</i> - choose, make.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}